skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: portugal squad helper
des: This is the squad helper for Portugal fans in EURO 2016 this summer. It provides basic bio for the 23 players in Portugal National Team. The User can ask "Can you tell me something about Cristiano Ronaldo?", Alexa will response with a short bio of Cristiano Ronaldo.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
